<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383608" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/wei.jpg" alt="" width="689" height="392" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/wei.jpg 689w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/wei-360x205.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 689px) 100vw, 689px" /></p>
