<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/12/100-usd-official-die-cast-poke-ball-the-wand-company-release-info">英国品牌推出 1：1 精灵球周边</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383609" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/100-usd-official-die-cast-poke-ball-the-wand-company-release-info-1.jpg" alt="" width="1800" height="1200" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/100-usd-official-die-cast-poke-ball-the-wand-company-release-info-1.jpg 1800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/100-usd-official-die-cast-poke-ball-the-wand-company-release-info-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/100-usd-official-die-cast-poke-ball-the-wand-company-release-info-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/100-usd-official-die-cast-poke-ball-the-wand-company-release-info-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px" /></p>
<p>英国周边制造商 The Wand Company 近日推出了官方授权的 1:1 尺寸的 Poké Ball，材质为金属，配有感应效果、彩色按钮和专属编号全息图认证。</p>
<p>这款精灵球定价为 100 美元（约人民币 655 元），目前已经开启预售，预计将于 2021 年 2 月 27 日的 Pokémon Day 发货。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.com/2020/12/netflix-black-mirror-charlie-brooker-mockumentary-2020">《黑镜》创作人打造基于 2020 年的伪纪录片</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383610" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/netflix-black-mirror-charlie-brooker-mockumentary-2020-001.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/netflix-black-mirror-charlie-brooker-mockumentary-2020-001.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/netflix-black-mirror-charlie-brooker-mockumentary-2020-001-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/netflix-black-mirror-charlie-brooker-mockumentary-2020-001-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/netflix-black-mirror-charlie-brooker-mockumentary-2020-001-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>演员 Hugh Grant 在接受采访时透露，他参与了《黑镜》创作人 Charlie Brooker 为 Netflix 打造的伪纪录片，内容基于 2020 年发生的事件。Grant 表示自己在影片中饰演一名历史学家。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>日本成辣条最大进口国</h4>
<p>据统计，2020 年下半年辣条出口额同比增长超 120%，出口至 160 国，海外购买辣条最多的国家依次为日本、新加坡、韩国、美国。</p>
<p>网友：「最好吃的还是小时候五毛钱一条的那种！」「完了，辣条会不会涨价，为什么我的宝藏一个个被挖出来。」「难道是当地的中国人买的？」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357582" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/thur-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.archdaily.cn/cn/952407/metalhands-bei-jing-qian-men-ka-pei-bei-jing-da-guan-jian-zhu-she-ji">Metalhands 咖啡 @ 北京·中国</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383463" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-2.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-2.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-2-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-2-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>Metalhands 咖啡位于北京前门的西打磨厂街，改造于一栋传统的青砖建筑。</p>
<p>设计团队在改造时，尽可能地保留了建筑原本的材质与肌理，「让新的新，旧的旧，从而产生一种新旧对比」。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383464" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>咖啡厅一楼设有三个拱券结构：第一层是不锈钢板拱券，在结构上支撑起原本老旧且存在安全隐患的墙面；第二层是混凝土拱券，设计团队在原始建筑的基础上涂刷了水泥漆，保持老房子岁月的质感；第三层是保留的外立面一致的青砖拱券。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1383467" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/rows.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="914" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/rows.jpg 2000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/rows-360x165.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/rows-768x351.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/rows-1024x468.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p>
<p>三层拱券的透视结构，让人仿佛沉浸在一种被历史包裹的氛围之下，一切旧的东西都以一种新的姿态呈现</p>